### Installation

test -f Makefile || {  # If Makefile is not yet generated, do:
	autoreconf -fi
	./configure
}

make maintainer-clean

## Edit to change the version:
: configure.ac
: README.md
: CHANGELOG
: weborf.1
: weborf.conf.5

autoreconf -fi

./configure

make

## Recommended:
make check

## With elevated permissions if required:
sudo make install

## In order to uninstall, might require elevated permission:
: make uninstall

